summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to land use and zoning; amending Plat 221W, page 7 of the Official Land Use Map to rezone property at 13726 15th Avenue Northeast, from Single Family 7200 (SF 7200) to Lowrise 3 (L-3) zone and accepting a Property Use and Development Agreement in connection therewith. (Petition of Bradley A. Hill, C.F. 298303)
